vocabInfos.mediumDef:
A man of the Ammonites living at the time of United Monarchy, first mentioned at 2Sa.23.37
§ Zelek = "fissure"
an Ammonite and a warrior for David
vocabInfos._es_Definition: amonita; guerrero; en tiempos del rey David
